      "text": "   \n  Weekly_Cap (WC)  =  (B × R) + (E × P)   \n\n  Per_Delivery_Cut =  WC / Projected_Weekly_Deliveries\n\n  Projected_Weekly_Deliveries = avg of last 4 weeks (rolling)\n",
